name: Gingerbread Lady
description:
She is all hand crafted made of Polyester & cotton fabric and filled with Polyester fiberfill and Poly pellets. Her face is hand stitched and her white zig zag on her body is hand painted with acrylic paint. Her clothes are also made of Polyester & cotton fabric. I am sure she could be washed however I have never put mine in the washer. Her dress and apron and bloomers can be washed on gentle in a pillow case and air dried. Each doll is handmade so may not be exact to another. At this time I have only one completed. I will have more very soon with Christmas Clothes. Intended
PURPOSES
